This is a profile-picture on hover feauture.
Here is the code!
Please do not publish this code anywhere however, you can use it for jobs and other stuff. 

HTML
<div class="image-container">
            <a href=""><img src="images/Github Logo 1.jpg" alt="Image"></a>
            <div class="overlay">
              <p>Huzi7</p>
            </div>
          </div>

CSS
  .image-container {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .image-container img {
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    border: 5px solid #e29a7d;
  }
  .image-container .overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #e29a7d;
    color: #fff;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .image-container:hover .overlay {
    opacity: 1;
  }
